race.comment: BIG TRUCKER (7) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Warragul over 400m behind Inflection Point (23.65) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. The form out of last race has been strong. Can bounce back. SWEET COIN BABE (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Warragul over 400m behind Donkey Fly (23.05) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Expected to feature in the finish. DUNSMORE FLYER (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Barking Blue (17.18) in a Grade 5. Winning chance. TILES AND WINE (3) is worth including after a top-three finish from the same draw most recently.
